                                    <ul>
                                        <li><b>Keep track of your sources:<=
/b></li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p>When working with a draft or an outl=
ine, taking notes and doing your best to copy citations is necessary. When =
you have a book or a journal with citation information, copy it to a safe p=
lace. Keeping track of your sources and page numbers makes it easier to wor=
k on your bibliography and eliminate plagiarism cases.</p>
                                    <ul>
